 {
  "text": "Hi everyone, let me tell you about a typical workday on our team. Our workday always starts at nine o'clock. First, we have a short stand-up meeting at nine fifteen. In this meeting, we talk about our tasks for the day. After the stand-up, we usually check our email and start our work. We often take a lunch break at twelve thirty. In the afternoon, we sometimes have one more meeting. And we never forget our reports: every report is due on Friday, before five o'clock. That is our normal day. It is busy, but we really like our routine!",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a2_listening_schedule.mp3"
